#

Pumpkin Seed Rice Bowl

30 min
$5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Pumpkin seeds

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A hearty and nutritious rice bowl topped with crunchy pumpkin seeds and fresh veggies, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • brown rice: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • pumpkin seeds: 1/4 cup
  • bell pepper: 1, diced
  • spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
